458.99,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"There''s actually a Reddit thread that pops up the next Tiva.","index":438,"end_time":1467.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1463.55,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"RingCentral pops up again, Dial Pad.","index":439,"end_time":1471.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1467.75,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So ring.","index":440,"end_time":1476.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1475.83,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Not a lot.","index":441,"end_time":1477.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1476.43,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"What''s interesting is basically it''s only Dial Pad and ringcentral who are showing as paid ads.","index":442,"end_time":1483.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1477.19,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Really?","index":443,"end_time":1483.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1483.27,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Then it basically just goes into articles.","index":444,"end_time":1486.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1484.32,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"If you scroll all the way down to the bottom of page one, are there more ads down at the bottom?","index":445,"end_time":1492.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1487.92,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"They''re the same ones again.","index":446,"end_time":1495,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1493.68,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"RingCentral and Dial Pad.","index":447,"end_time":1496.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1495,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So yeah, they''re just.","index":448,"end_time":1498.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1497.36,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"They have their budgets way jacked up high, like.","index":449,"end_time":1501.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1498.56,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":450,"end_time":1501.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1501.36,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"But I just found it interesting that there''s just not a lot of people who advertise on that.","index":451,"end_time":1505.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1501.68,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Basically it goes from that to a Reddit thread about replacement.","index":452,"end_time":1510.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1505.8,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"A Forbes article about replacement.","index":453,"end_time":1512.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1510.36,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":454,"end_time":1514.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1513.85,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"So technologyadvanced.com blog about replacement.","index":455,"end_time":1517.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1514.05,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":456,"end_time":1520.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1519.61,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"So for the paid ads, I mean, you know, we could be in the running to show up on that page, but our bid is not high enough.","index":457,"end_time":1527.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1520.01,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"And RingCentral has, you know, tons of ad groups about different topics that they are bidding high on.","index":458,"end_time":1534.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1527.93,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"So they.","index":459,"end_time":1534.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1534.25,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"My guess, my point on this is that are we going about this the wrong may.","index":460,"end_time":1540.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1534.85,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Maybe if we need to pop up, we should write some blog posts on replacing RingCentral to show up.","index":461,"end_time":1544.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1540.06,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Because some of this is.","index":462,"end_time":1545.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1544.42,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I mean, I have to guess some of this is organic.","index":463,"end_time":1547.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1545.34,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":464,"end_time":1548.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1548.5,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":465,"end_time":1549.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1548.94,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"If they''re not ads, then it''s an organic result.","index":466,"end_time":1551.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1549.22,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"And we could potentially bypass RingCentral advertising altogether if we could rank a blog Post about replacing RingCentral.","index":467,"end_time":1559.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1551.22,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yes.","index":468,"end_time":1559.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1559.02,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Right.","index":469,"end_time":1559.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1559.3,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And my point of that being is there was a Reddit article, there''s a open phone article, there''s a article by Forbes, there''s an article by WPBeginner.com about it.","index":470,"end_time":1571.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1559.54,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It basically is articles about all these page ones are Dial Pad ring central, then a bunch of articles and blog posts.","index":471,"end_time":1578.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1571.23,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So maybe if we want to rank, we just have to.","index":472,"end_time":1580.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1578.83,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I just got to rate 4 blog posts.","index":473,"end_time":1584.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1581.39,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"About it.","index":474,"end_time":1584.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1584.47,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And we, you know, we sit and wait and see if we rank.","index":475,"end_time":1586.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1584.83,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"t