1,"start_time":361.6,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"You''ll just see, like.","index":119,"end_time":362.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":361.92,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"You''ll see, like, my phone, for example, and the phone is fine.","index":120,"end_time":366.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":362.64,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"But you''ll see because I''m capturing on my computer, you''ll see a little bit of my desktop behind it.","index":121,"end_time":371.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":366.68,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"I see.","index":122,"end_time":372.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":371.96,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Okay.","index":123,"end_time":373.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":372.64,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"But we can use the videos as is.","index":124,"end_time":375.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":373.04,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Use the videos as is.","index":125,"end_time":376.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":375.64,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Okay.","index":126,"end_time":377.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":376.92,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Not my voiceover, obviously.","index":127,"end_time":380.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":377.56,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":128,"end_time":381.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":380.6,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Because the voiceover is me explaining what I would like to see and focus on.","index":129,"end_time":385,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":381.16,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Because ideally you take the video, but we, like, somehow make it look like we zoom in on certain points or we draw attention to certain actions that are happening.","index":130,"end_time":395,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":385,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"So I tried talking through that in.","index":131,"end_time":398.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":395.4,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text"