0.27,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"I can get it pulled up.","index":145,"end_time":453.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":452.51,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So can I. I have it up here somewhere.","index":146,"end_time":457.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":454.43,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Got it.","index":147,"end_time":460.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":459.71,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Speedy, you have the link or if you want to share your screen.","index":148,"end_time":465.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":461.39,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Computer is slow.","index":149,"end_time":466.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":465.71,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"I could share my screen, actually.","index":150,"end_time":468.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":467.23,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Okay.","index":151,"end_time":474.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":474.27,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Share screen, Share screen.","index":152,"end_time":476.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":474.83,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Share, share, share, share.","index":153,"end_time":477.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":476.56,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Okay, so I put new comments for scenes 6 through 10.","index":154,"end_time":483.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":478.08,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Put them all at the top here.","index":155,"end_time":486.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":484.72,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"So you''ll see like.","index":156,"end_time":488.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":487.36,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Like this one, for example.","index":157,"end_time":489.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":488.2,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"In fact, I''ll share audio, too, to verify that this is working.","index":158,"end_time":495.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":489.68,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"So, like, you would go here and you''ve got the video recording.","index":159,"end_time":500.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":495.44,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"You can see there''s an outline.","index":160,"end_time":502.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":500.68,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":161,"end_time":502.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":502.16,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Here.","index":162,"end_time":503.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":502.68,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"And you should be able to go here and download any of the GIFs that need to download.","index":163,"end_time":508.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":503.78,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"And then.","index":164,"end_time":509.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":509.3,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Okay, in this example, we''re looking at scene six.","index":165,"end_time":513.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":510.82,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"There''s gonna be two parts of scene six.","index":166,"end_time":514.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":513.38,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"We''re gonna show the mobile side and then we''re gonna show.","index":167,"end_time":516.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":514.82,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"So I''m like, findings completion.","index":168,"end_time":518.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":516.78,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Trying to talk through the intention here.","index":169,"end_time":520.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":518.42,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"This demo is gonna be slower than we want the act check themselves.","index":170,"end_time":524.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":520.62,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":171,"end_time":525.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":524.9,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"So I give, like, some verbal notes of, like, what I would love for us to like.","index":172,"end_time":529.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":525.38,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":173,"end_time":531.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":530.84,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"You know, it''s almost like the video pops up and we''re zooming and drawing attention in and stuff like that is.","index":174,"end_time":537.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":531.2,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"The text on the screen.","index":175,"end_time":539.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":537.56,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Okay?","index":176,"end_time":539.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":539.04,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":177,"end_time":540.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":540.44,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"So the stuff that you see here, for the most part, the videos are good to go.","index":178,"end_time":546.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":541.32,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"There''s moments like, for example.","index":179,"end_time":549.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":547,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"So, okay, in this one, we''re showing that you can capture a photo, but we would need to do some Hollywood magic and a photo here.","index":180,"end_time":562.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":553.08,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Swap that out with a photo.","index":181,"end_time":564.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":562.99,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Okay.","index":182,"end_time":564.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":564.35,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So there are moments in which I''m like, can you please, like, not show this thing and either, like, cut ahead to something else or replace it.","index":183,"end_time":574.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":565.71,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"But I tried to talk through all of that, like, as I was going.","index":184,"end_time":578.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":574.55,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Okay, that should work then.","index":185,"end_time":581.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":578.51,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Our team has gotten very familiar with a lot of your platform with those videos.","index":186,"end_time":589.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":582.71,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So I think these ones should.","index":187,"end_time":590.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":589.03,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, should go pretty well.","index":188,"end_time":592.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":590.95,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Thank them for their service.","index":189,"end_time":594.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":593.27,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"And yes, yes, the.","index":190,"end_time":598.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":594.47,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"The videos have been very helpful too.","index":191,"end_time":600.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":598.95,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Okay, so then we should be good.","index":192,"end_time":607.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":603.51,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"It sounds like, to get started on actions plans or are there any other videos you wanted to do for that one?","index":193,"end_time":614.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":607.51,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Action plans, I think is good.","index":194,"end_time":618.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":614.76,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"I took the same thing.","index":195,"end_time":619.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":618.76,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Like, you''ll see I linked it.","index":196,"end_time":621,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":619.68,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"I think the biggest thing that we''re going to have to kind of figure out is what parts of the videos would have to be, like, sped up or slowed down or like, how do we make the audio match?","index":197,"end_time":632.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":621,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Because, like, that my video demo, especially because I''m explaining stuff takes longer than the talk track.","index":198,"end_time":639.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":632.44,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"So I do think that there''s going to be some.","index":199,"end_time":641.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":639.74,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"With all of these.","index":200,"end_time":642.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":642.14,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"There''s going to be some.","index":201,"end_time":643.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":642.82,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"How do we make the timing work?","index":202,"end_time":646.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":643.5,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s why, you know, again, I tried to talk about what we''re trying to emphasize.","index":203,"end_time":651.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":646.62,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"That way the editing team can help with like, okay, so he just wants to show it being completed.","index":204,"end_time":657.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":651.62,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Boom.","index":205,"end_time":657.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":657.18,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Okay, we got to the completion side kind of thing.","index":206,"end_time":660.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":657.5,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Okay, yeah, that''s gonna.","index":207,"end_time":662.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":660.94,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"That''s probably what''s gonna be pretty time consuming on our side.","index":208,"end_time":666.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":662.78,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"But we''re good at the beginning just to use like some like, stock video to like, introduce things with text.","index":209,"end_time":675.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":667.9,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"And then we''ll start jumping into the actual platform like, pretty quickly after that.","index":210,"end_time":681.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":676.38,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Okay, we will.","index":211,"end_time":683.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":682.62,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"We''ll do another storyboard first, make sure we''ve got like, the right screenshots for everything, and then we''ll go from there.","index":212,"end_time":692.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":684.7,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Okay, great.","index":213,"end_time":693.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":692.79,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Okay, so then I think we''re good on videos.","index":214,"end_time":698.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":694.39,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Then we''ll just do a quick look at.","index":215,"end_time":701.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":699.99,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"At your portal.","index":216,"end_time":703.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":702.15,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So we''re looking really good.","index":217,"end_time":706.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":704.39,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"This is for your podcast contract.","index":218,"end_time":708.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":706.31,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Looking like really good on points for everything and just working on getting a backlog again here.","index":219,"end_time":715.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":708.95,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"But yeah, any questions or anything else you want to shout through?","index":220,"end_time":719.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":716.96,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, so not a marquee year for ease.","index":221,"end_time":724.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":720.56,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"So ownership is going to be tightening the budget, which means things are going to be put on the chopping block.","index":222,"end_time":732.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":726,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"I need to get videos done ASAP to show that there''s value here.","index":223,"end_time":741.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":733.68,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"So, like, ideally December, we can deliver these videos.","index":224,"end_time":748.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":742.92,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Like all of them.","index":225,"end_time":750.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":748.92,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Like, ideally would be all of them, if not either most of them or a path to more.","index":226,"end_time":757.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":750.2,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"It is likely that after these videos, if we''re not able to like, demonstrate, like it''s these are helpful assets and building more, that they''re going to get cut.","index":227,"end_time":769.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":758.44,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"So, like, I need something to go and say, like, this is what we''re doing this is what we''re using this time, energy and resources for.","index":228,"end_time":776.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":769.08,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":229,"end_time":777.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":777.14,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So that being said, I also have to prepare for the inevitable.","index":230,"end_time":783.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":780.1,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Like if it does come down to we''re cutting this.","index":231,"end_time":787.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":783.66,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"So I''ll need to just get refreshed on what your cancellation policy is because of that.","index":232,"end_time":795.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":788.9,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"I think it was like, you think.","index":233,"end_time":796.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":795.78,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"It would come for the podcast too, or are we mostly looking at like our video contract or all of the above?","index":234,"end_time":802.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":796.86,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So everything is tbd.","index":235,"end_time":806.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":803.84,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"I know Andrea wants to fight for both, but you know, she.","index":236,"end_time":810.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":806.08,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"If she has to cut something, it''ll be the videos after we delivered something.","index":237,"end_time":814.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":810.32,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"But I would say until I get more information, it''s kind of like nothing''s off the table at the moment.","index":238,"end_time":823.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":816.32,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"When are the decisions being made, man?","index":239,"end_time":827.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":824.99,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Ain''t that the question of the day?","index":240,"end_time":830.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":827.75,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"I don''t have a firm answer on that.","index":241,"end_time":833.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":831.47,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"I know the board meeting was yesterday, so I expect whatever guidance or direction to start being ideated on and put into motion pretty quickly.","index":242,"end_time":844.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":833.35,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Okay.","index":243,"end_time":845.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":844.91,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I hope to find out more like next week, but I don''t know, it''s just I gotta prepare for like stuff getting cut.","index":244,"end_time":853.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":845.71,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Okay.","index":245,"end_time":854.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":853.72,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So yes.","index":246,"end_time":856.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":855.16,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Would love to get some videos out and.","index":247,"end_time":858.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":856.36,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"And if we can''t get them all out, then a clear path of like how we''re gonna get them out.","index":248,"end_time":867.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":858.68,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":249,"end_time":868.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":867.64,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"And pretty much I''ve been told by Andrea, like, drop everything to get the videos done and out.","index":250,"end_time":876.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":868.2,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"So.","index":251,"end_time":876.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":876.29,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Okay, well, we will work as quickly as we can on them.","index":252,"end_time":883.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":877.49,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I know we''ve gone through like a lot of revisions and needed a lot of recordings from you to.","index":253,"end_time":889.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":883.65,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"To get these moving, but sounds like at the very least we can get moving on finishing the product video and the action plans video.","index":254,"end_time":902.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":889.25,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"And we''re.","index":255,"end_time":903.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":902.99,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":256,"end_time":904.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":903.71,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Steadily the other ones are coming along as well.","index":257,"end_time":906.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":904.07,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Let me just take a look at your contract really quick.","index":258,"end_time":913.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":909.83,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So your podcast contract, I''m not gonna lie, you got a deal of a lifetime with this.","index":259,"end_time":924.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":919.03,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Like, I have not seen any other clients get such a good deal.","index":260,"end_time":927.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":924.47,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":261,"end_time":928.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":928.07,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"So let''s.","index":262,"end_time":930.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":929.73,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"If I could put my.","index":263,"end_time":932.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":931.09,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I would keep that because you''ve got a killer deal.","index":264,"end_time":935.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":932.93,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"But I totally understand what the video stuff like.","index":265,"end_time":939.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":936.93,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Let''s wrap those up and see what we can do next there.","index":266,"end_time":942.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":939.29,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So the way your contract is set up is you''re on a three month renewal period and we need 45 days notice before the next period starts.","index":267,"end_time":954.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":942.29,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So your next period starts on December 8th.","index":268,"end_time":960.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":955.34,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So your renewal was October 24th.","index":269,"end_time":966.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":961.74,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So that''s like when we would have needed to know that you were going to cancel.","index":270,"end_time":969.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":966.66,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So then just 45 days after December 8th.","index":271,"end_time":974.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":971.02,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Then we''ll need to know.","index":272,"end_time":977.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":974.58,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Okay, what is 45 days after December 8th?","index":273,"end_time":980.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":978.06,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Usually does the math for me.","index":274,"end_time":983.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":982.25,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"But let''s see.","index":275,"end_time":986.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":983.57,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"That''s going to be January 22nd.","index":276,"end_time":996.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":993.77,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"January 22nd.","index":277,"end_time":997.369,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":996.41,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Okay.","index":278,"end_time":998.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":997.45,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"And that''s for the videos, the podcast, both.","index":279,"end_time":1002.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":999.37,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"That''s for your podcast.","index":280,"end_time":1004.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1002.65,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Let''s pull up your video contract.","index":281,"end_time":1006.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1004.33,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Okay.","index":282,"end_time":1007.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1007.08,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"So this one, the next term starts January 13th.","index":283,"end_time":1017.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1011.8,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So you would need to let us know by November 29th.","index":284,"end_time":1021.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1018.36,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Okay.","index":285,"end_time":1022.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1021.96,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"So that one''s coming up a bit sooner.","index":286,"end_time":1025.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1023.4,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"We can.","index":287,"end_time":1027.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1026.44,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"We can try and be a little flexible with things.","index":288,"end_time":1031.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1028.84,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Like, since that date''s coming up soon, I''ll let Justin and Tristan know what''s going on.","index":289,"end_time":1038.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1031.32,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, but.","index":290,"end_time":1042.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1040.89,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":291,"end_time":1043.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1042.57,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"And talking with Andrea, she wants to fight for the podcast.","index":292,"end_time":1046.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1043.93,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"She''s assuming she''s going to have to make cuts again.","index":293,"end_time":1050.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1047.37,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"She doesn''t have any direction.","index":294,"end_time":1052.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1050.17,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"And it''s likely videos would be on the cutting block.","index":295,"end_time":1058.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1052.97,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":296,"end_time":1059.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1058.97,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Okay.","index":297,"end_time":1060.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1060,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":298,"end_time":1060.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1060.36,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Well, we''ll at least try to go out with a bang.","index":299,"end_time":1065.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1062.72,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"We''ll get some good stuff going.","index":300,"end_time":1067.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1065.28,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"And that''s just until we stabilize.","index":301,"end_time":1070.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1068.08,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Right?","index":302,"end_time":1070.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1070.32,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Like, until.","index":303,"end_time":1071.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1070.68,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Until the grip gets unloosened, you know?","index":304,"end_time":1075.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1072.32,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yeah, but yeah, yeah, totally understand.","index":305,"end_time":1079.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1075.519,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Thanks for letting us know in advance, too.","index":306,"end_time":1081.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1079.68,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So we can try to move as quickly as we can.","index":307,"end_time":1084.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1081.52,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, for sure.","index":308,"end_time":1086.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1085.62,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"I definitely need to get some stuff out there.","index":309,"end_time":1089.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1086.3,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Cause it''s like the videos have, like, CEO attention now.","index":310,"end_time":1093.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1089.94,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Cause we got a new CEO came in and he chatted with sales.","index":311,"end_time":1096.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1093.78,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Sales.","index":312,"end_time":1097.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1097.3,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"What do you need to sell better?","index":313,"end_time":1098.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1097.7,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"And they said videos.","index":314,"end_time":1099.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1098.62,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"And so now it''s like, oh, get the videos out there.","index":315,"end_time":1103.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1099.78,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"You gotta get them done.","index":316,"end_time":1105.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1104.5,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Okay, so.","index":317,"end_time":1106.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1105.62,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"But there''s a positive in that.","index":318,"end_time":1107.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1106.66,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"In that if the videos are a hit, then maybe it''s not on the chopping block.","index":319,"end_time":1112.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1107.94,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":320,"end_time":1112.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1112.61,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Because if that''s what they''re saying they need.","index":321,"end_time":1114.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1112.85,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Right, Exactly.","index":322,"end_time":1115.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1114.93,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":323,"end_time":1116.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1116.21,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Which is why I want to get ahead of this as quickly as I can.","index":324,"end_time":1120.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1116.77,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":325,"end_time":1122.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1120.61,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I mean, we''ve been working on them lots, so we''ll just gotta tie the bow on it nicely and get it over the finish line.","index":326,"end_time":1130.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1122.01,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":327,"end_time":1132.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1130.37,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Sounds great.","index":328,"end_time":1133.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1132.53,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Well, thanks for chatting and yeah, we''ll be in touch.","index":329,"end_time":1136.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1133.21,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Sounds good.","index":330,"end_time":1137.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1137.01,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Okay, we''ll see you.","index":331,"end_time":1139.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1138.05,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"}],"dateString":"2025-11-12T21:30:00.000Z","host_email":"baylee.gunnell@marketersindemand.com","meeting_link":"https://us02web.zoom.us/j/82164087465?pwd=HIMrVfQh9H8oWdIxFsR0aU3slIkuOP.1","participants":["baylee.gunnell@marketersindemand.com,josh.santo@ease.io","josh.santo@ease.io"],"transcript_url":"https://app.fireflies.ai/view/01K9CWN2TT45F8EFDGR8XWNVNK","organizer_email":"baylee.gunnell@marketersindemand.com"}'::jsonb,
    '{"label":"negative","confidence":0.91,"bullets":["Flagged urgent need to finish videos before budget decisions threaten continuation of contract work.","Confirmed that video delivery delays risk project cancellation due to executive scrutiny and board pressure.","Set internal deadline to complete video assets by December in order to demonstrate ROI.","Clarified contract cancellation deadlines: November 29 for video, January 22 for podcast renewal.","Agreed to prioritize production of Action Plan and Product Overview videos with tighter editing turnaround."],"highlights":[{"quote":"Ownership is going to be tightening the budget, which means things are going to be put on the chopping block.","speaker":"Josh Santo"},{"quote":"Ideally December, we can deliver these videos.","speaker":"Josh Santo"},{"quote":"The videos have, like, CEO attention now...sales said videos...get the videos out there.","speaker":"Josh Santo"}],"topics":["risk","delivery","budget"],"model":"openai/gpt-4-1106-preview","version":1,"generated_at":"2025-11-13T00:00:00Z"}'::jsonb,
