sounds good to me.","index":204,"end_time":664.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":663.38,"speaker_name":"Monique King"},{"text":"Yeah, I agree.","index":205,"end_time":666.78,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":666.06,"speaker_name":"derey"},{"text":"So, okay, so we''ll work on getting all of these done and then send them over.","index":206,"end_time":674.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":668.94,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":207,"end_time":676.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":676.19,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And that''s an email campaign.","index":208,"end_time":678.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":676.91,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Primarily.","index":209,"end_time":678.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":678.27,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"It''s people click on the emails.","index":210,"end_time":680.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":678.87,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Those are the ones you''re going to send that second email to.","index":211,"end_time":682.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":680.43,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"People that click on the emails or any data we have on website visits, for example.","index":212,"end_time":688.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":684.19,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":213,"end_time":689.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":688.91,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":214,"end_time":690.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":689.79,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Basically all the data we''re collecting, just making sure we keep reaching out to those people.","index":215,"end_time":695.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":690.509,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":216,"end_time":697.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":696.59,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":217,"end_time":701.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":701.08,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then for your data.","index":218,"end_time":703.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":702.36,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So the website stats still look a little low.","index":219,"end_time":706.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":703.96,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"As that ABM campaign comes to an end, less people are clicking on the links and coming to the site.","index":220,"end_time":712.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":706.92,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"This refreshed campaign, as well as the nurture strategy, we should see those start to go back up for LinkedIn ads.","index":221,"end_time":722.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":713.32,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"We saw the cost per click reduce to 9.8 dollars versus 13.7 last year, period.","index":222,"end_time":729.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":722.24,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"That''s after changing the audience we''re targeting.","index":223,"end_time":732.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":730,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So seems like it''s more relevant to them.","index":224,"end_time":734.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":732.08,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"But then also we''re updating the creatives that we''re pushing out.","index":225,"end_time":739.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":735.2,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"We talked about that last time, since they''ve been running for a while, just changing them up a bit, and then we should see that reduce even more.","index":226,"end_time":745.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":740,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":227,"end_time":746.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":746,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"All right.","index":228,"end_time":749.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":749.12,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Those were my main notes for today.","index":229,"end_time":752.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":750.4,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Anything else that you wanted to cover.","index":230,"end_time":754.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":752.56,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Monique?","index":231,"end_time":760.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":759.93,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Dave, what are your thoughts?","index":232,"end_time":761.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":760.41,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Nothing.","index":233,"end_time":765.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":764.73,"speaker_name":"Monique King"},{"text":"Nothing on my end.","index":234,"end_time":766.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":765.21,"speaker_name":"Monique King"},{"text":"Yeah, that all Sounds good.","index":235,"end_time":769.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":767.93,"speaker_name":"Monique King"},{"text":"All right.","index":236,"end_time":771.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":770.65,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Dave and Monique, have you guys connected yet?","index":237,"end_time":775.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":773.05,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah, we connected last week.","index":238,"end_time":778.41,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":776.65,"speaker_name":"derey"},{"text":"Okay.","index":239,"end_time":779.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":778.89,"speaker_name":"Monique King"},{"text":"Dave, have you been able to get in touch with Hannah?","index":240,"end_time":783.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":781.38,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"No.","index":241,"end_time":784.98,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":784.58,"speaker_name":"derey"},{"text":"So I''ve sent out an email in a text.","index":242,"end_time":787.78,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":785.54,"speaker_name":"derey"},{"text":"I''ll follow up today.","index":243,"end_time":789.46,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":788.26,"speaker_name":"derey"},{"text":"I''ll shoot her both an email and a text today.","index":244,"end_time":792.66,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":789.62,"speaker_name":"derey"},{"text":"Okay.","index":245,"end_time":794.18,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":793.54,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"You might just give her a phone call, too, and leave a message, see what she.","index":246,"end_time":797.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":794.34,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"She does there.","index":247,"end_time":798.18,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":797.38,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay.","index":248,"end_time":799.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":798.98,"speaker_name":"Monique King"},{"text":"All right.","index":249,"end_time":802.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":802.18,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah, the.","index":250,"end_time":803.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":802.66,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Our main goal is we''ve got to start increasing our demos.","index":251,"end_time":806.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":803.3,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"That''s the bottom line.","index":252,"end_time":808.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":806.74,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And.","index":253,"end_time":808.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":808.18,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And, I mean, we''re just not getting enough demos.","index":254,"end_time":812.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":808.6,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":255,"end_time":813.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":812.92,"speaker_name":"Monique King"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":256,"end_time":814.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":814.36,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I hope that this free trial offer is enticing to get people to try.","index":257,"end_time":819.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":814.72,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":258,"end_time":822.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":821.88,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":259,"end_time":823.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":822.6,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay, let''s see what