    NULL,
    '{"id":"01K9YVGVKMFHGD1YY8RX6EJ2YB","title":"GMT20251112-155923_Recording_1920x1080.mp4","summary":{"notes":"## **Marketing Program Development and Campaign Execution**\n\nThe team is launching a modular thought leadership program for the **WIMS product**, starting with a **pre-recorded webinar on November 25th at 11:00 AM** to simplify complex product training (08:52).  \n- The webinar will be live-like with polls but pre-recorded, lasting about **20 minutes** to respect user time and attention.  \n- Barb highlighted the aim to break down the large platform into smaller, focused content chunks to improve customer understanding and sales upsell opportunities.  \n- This program will evolve into a nurture campaign combining webinars, ROI calculators, case studies, and regional events to engage prospects and customers continuously.  \n- The initial outreach targets **100-150 attendees** drawn from sponsorship events, with future campaigns planned for sustained engagement.\n\nThe current system uses **Marketo for event invites and reminders**, transitioning to **Constant Contact** for post-event outreach to improve follow-up efficiency (28:17).  \n- Barb manages a manual but effective Constant Contact workflow to nurture registrants after the event, improving on the minimal existing follow-up process.  \n- The team plans to bridge Marketo and HubSpot, with Marketo as the last tool for event invitations before fully moving to HubSpot for lead nurturing.  \n- Tristan’s team will help design and replicate this workflow in HubSpot once it is ready, ensuring smooth campaign continuity and scalability.\n\nLead scoring and tracking are under overhaul to better qualify leads from events and digital interactions (33:36).  \n- Barb described the current **lead scoring as a “horror show”**, with unclear criteria and poor integration between systems.  \n- The team is starting with defining lead sources and scoring rules, with **12-15 lead sources** identified to replace the current two, aligning marketing and sales expectations.  \n- A **cutoff date of October 26th** is set for Marketo campaigns before fully transitioning to HubSpot-led campaigns.\n\n## **Website Infrastructure and Content Management**\n\nThe website currently lacks a strategic content structure and a staging environment, which hinders campaign execution and content management (06:22).  \n- Barb confirmed New North has **WordPress access** but noted the current site editing process is transactional, with no staging environment or strategic content control.  \n- The hosting details and staging options remain unknown, with Barb assigned to clarify and potentially establish a staging site to reduce risk during content updates.  \n- The lack of workflow means content changes go directly live, increasing risk and limiting quality control.\n\nThe team identified key content gaps and mismanagement on the site, including outdated case studies and poor content mapping (21:40).  \n- Barb discovered **13 new case studies** sitting unused while older materials remain live, indicating missed marketing opportunities.  \n- A content mapping exercise is scheduled to better organize the site’s assets and improve user navigation and content relevance.  \n- The goal is to create a dedicated WIMS program section featuring webinars, knowledge series, and product-linked content blocks to increase visibility and engagement.\n\nAn analysis and recommendation document will be delivered before **Thanksgiving** to propose site structure improvements and integration of the WIMS program (24:14).  \n- This will include a revised sitemap, suggested language, and potential WordPress custom post types for dynamic content linking.  \n- The intent is to connect product pages with relevant content to drive lead nurturing and customer education more effectively.\n\n## **Technology Stack and System Integration**\n\nThe team is evaluating the marketing technology stack for simplification and integration to support automation and data flow (17:18).  \n- Current tools include **BigMarker for webinars**, **Marketo for marketing automation**, **Constant Contact for email campaigns**, and an upcoming **HubSpot implementation** planned for early 2024.  \n- Barb stressed the need to retire unused tools to streamline operations and reduce complexity, with Riverside video recording set to activate December 1st but possibly replaced if redundant.  \n- The team will consider building a custom app or webhook to connect BigMarker attendance data directly into HubSpot workflows for better automation and lead scoring.\n\nSalesforce integration and lead management processes are being redesigned to align with HubSpot’s capabilities (36:05).  \n- Barb identified **8 active Marketo forms** on the site that currently feed Salesforce with leads, requiring migration or redesign to work with HubSpot.  \n- The team plans to deprecate the Salesforce lead object in favor of using contacts classified by lifecycle stage, simplifying data management and reducing licensing costs.  \n- A detailed recommendation document will be produced explaining the rationale and next steps for syncing rules and system handoffs.\n\n## **Process Improvements and Operational Readiness**\n\nThe marketing team is shifting from ad-hoc, manual campaign execution to a more strategic, automated nurture approach (25:31).  \n- Barb emphasized starting with a **linear nurture sequence** triggered by webinar registration and attendance to provide timely, relevant follow-up content.  \n- This approach addresses low engagement volumes and builds a foundation for future ongoing newsletters or multi-touch campaigns once volume increases.  \n- The team is cautious about holiday season timing, planning to pause major campaign launches during the **U.S. Thanksgiving period** and resume in December and January.\n\nThe marketing ops team, including Guiller Gay, is tasked with data migration, workflow checks, and ensuring system readiness to support these campaigns (00:39).  \n- Guiller will oversee data migration and workflow validation to ensure smooth transitions between Marketo, BigMarker, and HubSpot systems.  \n- Barb requested help to review and improve current lead scoring and campaign flows based on the upcoming content mapping and system audits.  \n- The team will provide access to existing Constant Contact campaigns to replicate and improve workflows in HubSpot, with a focus on practical, small-scale wins before scaling.\n\n## **Timelines and Milestones**\n\nThe first key milestone is the **November 25th webinar launch**, marking the program’s public start and a test of systems integration and nurture flows (08:52).  \n- The **content mapping exercise begins Monday following the meeting**, aiming to clarify lead sources, scoring, and content organization (32:17).  \n- A draft analysis and recommendation report on website and campaign structure will be delivered before **Thanksgiving** to guide next steps (34:48).  \n- HubSpot implementation timelines remain flexible but are expected to ramp up after the holiday season, with Marketo phased out progressively by late Q4 2023 or early 2024.","outline":null,"keywords":["HubSpot implementation","webinar nurturing","lead scoring","marketing automation","website content strategy","BigMarker integration"],"overview":"- **Webinar Launch:** Pre-recorded webinar for WIMS on November 25th aims to simplify product training for customers.  \n- **Content Structuring:** Team to address website content gaps by organizing outdated case studies and improving user navigation.  \n- **Tech Stack Overhaul:** Evaluating tools for integration, with HubSpot roll-out targeting early 2024 to streamline marketing operations.  \n- **Lead Scoring Update:** Redefining lead scoring and sources to enhance qualification from events, targeting 12-15 lead sources.  \n- **Process Improvement:** Shifting to automated nurture campaigns to boost engagement, pausing major launches during the U.S. Thanksgiving.  \n- **Upcoming Deadlines:** Analysis report on website structure due before Thanksgiving, with flexible HubSpot migration post-holiday.","action_items":"\n**Barb**\nAsk James for hosting details and potential staging environment for WordPress website (07:33)\nShare newly found case studies and centralized content inventory with the team (21:40)\nProvide Constant Contact access to the team to review current nurture sequences (31:01)\nConfirm Marketo forms inventory and plan migration approach (35:00)\n\n**Tristan Pelligrino**\nConduct analysis of existing website structure to suggest improvements for the pillars program placement and visibility, including potential revised site map and custom post type implementation on WordPress (18:55)\nAssist with designing and building nurture campaigns in Constant Contact as an interim step before HubSpot migration (31:01)\nCollaborate on lead source definition and lead scoring framework during content mapping sessions starting Monday (33:35)\nHelp define syncing rules between Marketo, HubSpot, and Salesforce for lead/contact data and streamline lead process (35:00)\n\n**Guille/Gay**\nManage marketing operations, including data migration, checking data and workflows related to HubSpot and current systems (00:00)\n"},"duration":38.599998474121094,"speakers":[],"sentences":[{"text":"Hey, Tristan, what''s going on today?","index":0,"end_time":42.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":39.45,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"How you doing?","index":1,"end_time":43.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":42.77,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Doing well, thank you.","index":2,"end_time":46.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":44.25,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"How are you?","index":3,"end_time":46.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":46.29,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Good, good.","index":4,"end_time":48.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":47.21,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Doing well.","index":5,"end_time":48.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":48.05,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Doing well.","index":6,"end_time":49.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":48.89,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, we got some, some notes from Barb here on some projects she wants to.","index":7,"end_time":57.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":52.18,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So we have like two contracts with aquatic informatics.","index":8,"end_time":61.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":57.94,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"One''s a project and then the other is the HubSpot implementation.","index":9,"end_time":64.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":61.26,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So we wanted to talk today about some of the projects she wants help on.","index":10,"end_time":67.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":64.22,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s just a two month project and we''re kind of.","index":11,"end_time":70.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":67.5,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"They lost a marketing team member and so they wanted us to come in and fill, fill, fill in a little bit for the last two months.","index":12,"end_time":78.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":70.98,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Oh, good.","index":13,"end_time":79.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":79.29,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, so they''re kind of just some random things.","index":14,"end_time":84.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":80.09,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"They want help, you know, setting up some, some email campaigns and things like that.","index":15,"end_time":88.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":84.21,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So we''ll, we''ll learn a little bit more about what that includes.","index":16,"end_time":94.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":89.13,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Let me send this to you so you have.","index":17,"end_time":101.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":94.09,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It.","index":18,"end_time":104.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":104.74,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Barb.","index":19,"end_time":164.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":164.44,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Good morning.","index":20,"end_time":165.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":164.92,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Good morning.","index":21,"end_time":166.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":166.36,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Hey, Tristan.","index":22,"end_time":167.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":166.96,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"How are you doing today?","index":23,"end_time":169,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":167.88,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Hanging in there.","index":24,"end_time":170.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":169.8,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"How are you doing there?","index":25,"end_time":171.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":170.64,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Good, Doing well, Doing well.","index":26,"end_time":172.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":171.72,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I got Guille on the call too.","index":27,"end_time":174.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":172.88,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"She was on the last one, but we did like a rapid fire start, so we didn''t do anything.","index":28,"end_time":179.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":174.32,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We just got into it.","index":29,"end_time":182.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":181.24,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So yeah, let''s go.","index":30,"end_time":184.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":182.76,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But, but yeah, Gay works on our marketing operation stuff.","index":31,"end_time":189.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":185.24,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So that''s why I wanted to, to pull her in on the last meeting.","index":32,"end_time":193.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":189.1,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"She''ll be working on the data migration, you know, checking data and workflows, all that good stuff.","index":33,"end_time":199.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":193.22,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So today I do want to touch on our last meeting, make sure we have next step there.","index":34,"end_time":205.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":199.94,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But then I know, Barb, we wanted to talk about some of the, the projects that you had like related to our other sow that we have.","index":35,"end_time":212.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":205.98,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So go through both of those things.","index":36,"end_time":214.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":212.66,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Where would you like to start?","index":37,"end_time":217.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":216.42,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Have your email pulled up.","index":38,"end_time":218.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":217.42,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Is that the best place?","index":39,"end_time":219.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":218.66,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Do you think that one''s probably faster?","index":40,"end_time":222.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":219.62,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"The one from last night?","index":41,"end_time":223.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":222.42,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yes.","index":42,"end_time":224.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":224.02,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yep.","index":43,"end_time":226.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":224.66,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So what I tried to do and I''ll just dive right in.","index":44,"end_time":229.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":226.9,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Nice to meet you again.","index":45,"end_time":231.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":229.82,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Is it.","index":46,"end_time":233.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":232.98,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"How do you pronounce your name?","index":47,"end_time":235.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":234.02,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Guiller.","index":48,"end_time":237.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":236.74,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Gaye.","index":49,"end_time":238.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":237.7,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s beautiful.","index":50,"end_time":239.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":238.3,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":51,"end_time":240.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":240.5,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Nice to meet you.","index":52,"end_time":241.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":240.9,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So if you look at the original sow and I know with New north we, we move things around the way that we need to.","index":53,"end_time":248.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":242.5,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Right.","index":54,"end_time":249.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":248.96,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So they''re signed, they''re in with AP and.","index":55,"end_time":252.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":249.28,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But then I looked at it last night and I thought, I think we''re a little soon.","index":56,"end_time":256.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":252.8,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Like I really focused on the new sow to be ready for Q1, get the campaigns in place, help us with two programs, some ABM as well as some nurture programs with the four pillars program that we have.","index":57,"end_time":270.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":256.32,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"The challenge with doing all of that is one, we don''t have the new system ready.","index":58,"end_time":275.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":271.04,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And also we have.","index":59,"end_time":276.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":275.4,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"All the assets are still in development.","index":60,"end_time":278.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":277.18,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So I think we''re a little early on those.","index":61,"end_time":281.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":280.06,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Maybe we can, you know, park those until December, but that''s why I took a look at maybe some infrastructure that we are missing for when these assets come due.","index":62,"end_time":292.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":282.7,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And that''s why if you want to pull up the.","index":63,"end_time":295.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":293.02,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That''s what got me to the three stages that I sent to you last night.","index":64,"end_time":299.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":295.58,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":65,"end_time":300.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":299.74,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So I''ve got.","index":66,"end_time":301.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":300.54,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So the first stage here.","index":67,"end_time":304.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":301.74,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So landing page for the pillars of productivity.","index":68,"end_time":307.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":304.81,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That''s the WIMS product.","index":69,"end_time":308.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":307.33,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It is, yeah.","index":70,"end_time":310.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":309.09,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yep.","index":71,"end_time":310.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":310.45,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So we''ve got the first one, dashboards.","index":72,"end_time":312.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":310.93,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s.","index":73,"end_time":312.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":312.49,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s primitive, trust me.","index":74,"end_time":315.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":313.25,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''m going through custom contact and.","index":75,"end_time":317.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":315.01,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And big marker and.","index":76,"end_time":319.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":317.65,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But it''s.","index":77,"end_time":320.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":320.21,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s 20 minutes in and out.","index":78,"end_time":322.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":320.85,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And we want to.","index":79,"end_time":323.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":322.53,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Is.","index":80,"end_time":323.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":323.49,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Is so long as we have content, that''s what we want to keep doing.","index":81,"end_time":330.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":323.85,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So we want to.","index":82,"end_time":331.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":330.21,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We won''t do one in December, but, you know, it''s basically with dashboards and then come January, what is the next one?","index":83,"end_time":338.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":331.17,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"What is the next one?","index":84,"end_time":339.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":338.35,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And it''s taking this massive behemoth of a platform and it''s just cutting it up into a million pieces and saying, let''s.","index":85,"end_time":346.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":339.39,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Let''s try not to boil the ocean.","index":86,"end_time":348.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":346.27,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You know, let''s.","index":87,"end_time":349.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":348.67,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Let''s strip it apart, have, you know, a conversation and narrative around each of those things and carry it through the year.","index":88,"end_time":357.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":349.55,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"As long as we have pillars to be able to do that.","index":89,"end_time":360.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":357.71,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But I started with four.","index":90,"end_time":361.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":360.31,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Could be 14.","index":91,"end_time":362.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":361.97,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But it''s four at the moment.","index":92,"end_time":364.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":362.69,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":93,"end_time":364.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":364.41,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And Barb, so how.","index":94,"end_time":366.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":365.01,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"How do you.","index":95,"end_time":366.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":366.49,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Vision.","index":96,"end_time":367.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":366.89,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Because I know you have someone now that''s maintaining the website.","index":97,"end_time":370.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":367.21,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Is that right?","index":98,"end_time":371.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":370.61,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Because he was on one of our first calls.","index":99,"end_time":373.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":371.57,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":100,"end_time":374.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":373.73,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So, you guys, New north has WordPress access now, and I''ll have to talk to Vivian about how we''re going to divide and conquer.","index":101,"end_time":382.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":375.57,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And, you know, so this brings us into kind of the next stage as well.","index":102,"end_time":387.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":382.81,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"When I say next stage, it''s the strategy for 2026 to say, okay, how are we resourcing this?","index":103,"end_time":394.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":387.97,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Who''s doing what?","index":104,"end_time":395.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":394.58,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Do we need James to be posting things?","index":105,"end_time":398.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":395.58,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I mean, I go in and change the content.","index":106,"end_time":399.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":398.26,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Is that the best way to do it?","index":107,"end_time":402.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":400.74,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Probably not.","index":108,"end_time":403.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":402.58,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You know, it goes straight into production.","index":109,"end_time":405.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":403.54,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"There''s no staging.","index":110,"end_time":406.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":405.42,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Just a little fun fact there.","index":111,"end_time":408.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":406.98,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But.","index":112,"end_time":408.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":408.66,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But also there''s, you know, I sent him over a massive list this morning.","index":113,"end_time":413.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":410.5,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"He''s Very transactional is what I''m trying to get across.","index":114,"end_time":415.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":413.86,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"There''s not a lot of strategy there.","index":115,"end_time":418.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":416.58,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s like, he''s great technically, but, hey, James, could you please do this?","index":116,"end_time":422.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":418.06,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And then he does it.","index":117,"end_time":423.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":422.51,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But, you know, when Vivian looks at it, he''s like, well, you know, he sends us these progress reports that I sent to New north last week and said, you know, these are the things we want to add to our future data box.","index":118,"end_time":433.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":423.87,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"To say, okay, this is what we''re tracking every day.","index":119,"end_time":435.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":433.47,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And you guys do that?","index":120,"end_time":436.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":435.35,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You do that.","index":121,"end_time":437.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":436.91,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":122,"end_time":438.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":438.27,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But he doesn''t tell us why things are happening.","index":123,"end_time":440.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":438.71,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s like, okay, well, this happened.","index":124,"end_time":442.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":440.79,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Hey, take a look at this.","index":125,"end_time":443.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":442.59,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"This spiked.","index":126,"end_time":444.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":443.63,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Why, like, we don''t.","index":127,"end_time":445.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":444.63,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We.","index":128,"end_time":446.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":445.75,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So we don''t.","index":129,"end_time":446.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":446.23,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I guess.","index":130,"end_time":447.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":446.91,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Short answer.","index":131,"end_time":447.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":447.39,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I don''t know if we''re going to keep them.","index":132,"end_time":448.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":447.87,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":133,"end_time":450.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":449.59,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So.","index":134,"end_time":451.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":451.19,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But you can go in there and change anything you want.","index":135,"end_time":453.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":451.75,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Like, you don''t have to ask his permission.","index":136,"end_time":455.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":453.75,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And so we do have WordPress.","index":137,"end_time":457.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":456.07,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So the one thing.","index":138,"end_time":458.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":457.51,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Do you know where it''s hosted?","index":139,"end_time":459.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":458.39,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Because we don''t have.","index":140,"end_time":461.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":459.83,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And that''s something I would like to have, too.","index":141,"end_time":463.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":461.11,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Like, sure.","index":142,"end_time":464.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":463.27,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Maybe there is a staging environment we can stand up pretty quickly.","index":143,"end_time":468.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":464.55,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Or do you have the hosting information on your side?","index":144,"end_time":470.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":468.03,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"No, I don''t.","index":145,"end_time":472.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":471.79,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''d have to ask him, but I will.","index":146,"end_time":474.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":472.35,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''ll ask him this afternoon.","index":147,"end_time":475.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":474.35,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay.","index":148,"end_time":476.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":475.95,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, because that''s something.","index":149,"end_time":478.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":477.55,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You know how that works, Barb.","index":150,"end_time":480.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":478.63,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s always good to have it there, and then if you screw up, it''s.","index":151,"end_time":483.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":480.07,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s okay.","index":152,"end_time":484.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":483.51,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, exactly.","index":153,"end_time":486.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":484.91,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay, so.","index":154,"end_time":488.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":487.15,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So you''ve got some things you want to do.","index":155,"end_time":490.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":488.35,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"There''s probably an area on the website that we create.","index":156,"end_time":493.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":490.67,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It looks like this is.","index":157,"end_time":494.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":493.47,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s more of a.","index":158,"end_time":496.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":495.47,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"A pillar program, not necessarily bucketed with webinars.","index":159,"end_time":501.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":497.4,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Right.","index":160,"end_time":501.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":501.08,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s more of like a training series or like knowledge base almost of the product.","index":161,"end_time":507.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":501.32,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Because this is, like, for folks that already are in the product.","index":162,"end_time":512.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":507.44,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Is this more like customer success or.","index":163,"end_time":514.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":512.04,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"No, it''s both.","index":164,"end_time":516.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":514.44,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So the first one starting is with our senior technical person who knows dashboards, so she''s internal.","index":165,"end_time":521.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":516.52,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So let''s take that as an example.","index":166,"end_time":523.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":522.12,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We''re starting.","index":167,"end_time":524.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":523.92,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We call it a webinar, but it''s.","index":168,"end_time":525.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":524.48,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s for lack of anywhere else to put it.","index":169,"end_time":528,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":526,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Share my screen in front of us.","index":170,"end_time":531.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":529.84,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":171,"end_time":532.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":531.8,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And I can.","index":172,"end_time":532.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":532.04,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I can go pretty quick here.","index":173,"end_time":533.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":532.52,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"There it is.","index":174,"end_time":536.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":535.44,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So, you know, it''s in the webinar series because we have nowhere else to put it and it''s not live.","index":175,"end_time":541.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":536.16,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''m actually recording it with her and a team ahead of time.","index":176,"end_time":545.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":541.84,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We don''t have.","index":177,"end_time":546.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":545.68,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"In the future it would be.","index":178,"end_time":548.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":547.44,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We''d want to use Riverside.","index":179,"end_time":549.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":548.64,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But I don''t.","index":180,"end_time":550.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":549.96,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I have the go ahead.","index":181,"end_time":551.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":550.8,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I think I said I have it.","index":182,"end_time":552.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":551.84,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I don''t physically have it yet.","index":183,"end_time":554.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":552.88,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That''s for December.","index":184,"end_time":555.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":554.24,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But I have it.","index":185,"end_time":556.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":555.04,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I just have to go get it.","index":186,"end_time":557.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":556.33,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So we''d want to have that program to be ongoing.","index":187,"end_time":561.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":558.73,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"As far as thought leadership basically is what this is right now.","index":188,"end_time":564.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":561.33,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"This is very rudimentary.","index":189,"end_time":566.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":564.85,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s, it''s a few slides, it''s a live demo through big marker and it''s 20 minutes in and out.","index":190,"end_time":574.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":566.97,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And that''s what we want to do is just like it''s a how to program to say, you know, you don''t have to sit here for an hour, three hours in a training program, 20 minutes, here''s what you do, here''s why you do it, let''s get in, let''s go to the next thing.","index":191,"end_time":584.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":574.01,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And so we want to build up that program as it''s thought leadership, but it''s also modular and so they can cross sell and upsell.","index":192,"end_time":592.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":585.52,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And I mean it''s just such a beat like most of these programs are.","index":193,"end_time":596.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":592.8,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s not an iPhone, you know, it''s, it''s a beast.","index":194,"end_time":598.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":596.44,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And it''s just like you''re trying to sell this.","index":195,"end_time":602.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":599.04,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I don''t even know what metaphor to put in like a Lamborghini.","index":196,"end_time":606.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":602.8,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Sometimes you just need a bus pass.","index":197,"end_time":607.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":606.28,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Right.","index":198,"end_time":607.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":607.6,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So it''s, it''s, it''s just too big to sell all at once.","index":199,"end_time":612.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":607.88,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So we wanted to put together this program that split it into chunks.","index":200,"end_time":617.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":613.49,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Cool.","index":201,"end_time":618.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":618.05,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So I like this.","index":202,"end_time":619.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":618.45,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So these are, these are pre recorded essentially webinars that folks will register and then tell me what happens after they register.","index":203,"end_time":628.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":619.73,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Like what''s the experience like that you envision there?","index":204,"end_time":631.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":628.57,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":205,"end_time":632.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":632.21,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So, well, this is going to be pre hub spot, I think.","index":206,"end_time":636.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":632.65,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So this is on the 25th.","index":207,"end_time":637.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":636.21,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We won''t be ready to go yet, but what I want to be able to do.","index":208,"end_time":640.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":637.29,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So let''s say there''s 100 people, they all have to opt in.","index":209,"end_time":644.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":640.77,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We''ll invite them to the next one.","index":210,"end_time":646.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":644.35,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But also what else is it?","index":211,"end_time":648.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":646.03,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We have countless case studies, ROI calculators, health assessments that we need to score differently right now.","index":212,"end_time":655.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":648.07,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Well, you heard the horror show.","index":213,"end_time":657.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":655.31,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That is our lead scoring, I think.","index":214,"end_time":660.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":657.59,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, it''s a bit of a wreck.","index":215,"end_time":663.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":661.31,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So we''re fixing everything.","index":216,"end_time":664.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":663.07,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Right.","index":217,"end_time":664.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":664.11,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Which is fine, we''ll get there.","index":218,"end_time":665.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":664.39,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But it''s like we really want to have a program that is a step process that says, okay, we can see this prospect or customer.","index":219,"end_time":674.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":665.95,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Customer.","index":220,"end_time":674.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":674.25,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"If they''re upgrading or cross selling through a system that makes sense, we can''t see that right now.","index":221,"end_time":680.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":674.61,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So this would be, let''s say we have a hundred people.","index":222,"end_time":683.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":680.25,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"What are we doing?","index":223,"end_time":683.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":683.05,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That''s a campaign.","index":224,"end_time":684.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":683.81,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"What are we doing with these hundred people?","index":225,"end_time":686.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":684.57,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We have assets evaluations, ROI calculators, phone calls, events.","index":226,"end_time":692.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":686.41,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We have regional, like we have 135 regional events across the US every year.","index":227,"end_time":697.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":692.45,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And all of those things are not happening right now.","index":228,"end_time":700.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":697.37,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Nothing.","index":229,"end_time":700.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":700.13,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Well, this isn''t even happening.","index":230,"end_time":702.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":701.03,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"This is the first thing.","index":231,"end_time":703.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":702.23,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So it''s to develop a program, call it a nurture if you will, but it''s an, it''s a in person digital thought leadership program that will continue to grow for wims.","index":232,"end_time":717.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":703.99,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And it''s just one program.","index":233,"end_time":719.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":718.07,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s not an abm.","index":234,"end_time":720.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":719.27,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s, you know, people that we have in the system connecting them to social, which we don''t do a very good job of really any of this right now.","index":235,"end_time":728.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":720.47,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But does that make sense?","index":236,"end_time":729.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":728.31,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, I like it a lot.","index":237,"end_time":732.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":730.55,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So, because you know us, I mean to have a pillar program in play, like that''s, that''s like what you need right, in order to nurture these folks.","index":238,"end_time":740.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":732.63,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So the, the foundation makes, makes sense there.","index":239,"end_time":743.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":740.23,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Do you envision.","index":240,"end_time":745.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":744.23,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So if someone, I think there''s two paths that we could go on.","index":241,"end_time":748.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":745.27,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"If they go register for the webinar, they, they get access to that webinar through, I''m assuming either an email with a link to a landing page or do they get access immediately where that''s the redirect page that they land on?","index":242,"end_time":763.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":748.67,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":243,"end_time":764.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":763.83,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So the people who attend live, so if they register at 11 o'', clock, it''s going to look live to them.","index":244,"end_time":770.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":764.39,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Now people who know what they''re doing know it''s not live, but you know, it''s going to look live with polls and you know, with people, etc.","index":245,"end_time":778.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":770.91,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But that''s the first time that we will show.","index":246,"end_time":781.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":779.35,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You have to register to actually see it the first time, November 25th at 11 o'', clock, right after.","index":247,"end_time":786.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":781.15,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And they each get a personalized link through big marker.","index":248,"end_time":789.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":786.9,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And then after that, if you registered or attended, we flip that into an on demand still.","index":249,"end_time":798.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":789.38,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s called a webinar, but I just hate that.","index":250,"end_time":800.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":798.26,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But it, we flip it to on demand and then you get a, everybody gets a link from the website with, you know, we put together another UTM and, and just say okay, now they''ve gone to the website to see it and now we have to register those people that if they attended, what happens to them?","index":251,"end_time":820.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":800.18,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"If they didn''t attend, they will get the link afterwards.","index":252,"end_time":823.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":820.9,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Then what happens to them?","index":253,"end_time":824.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":823.62,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"What''s happening to them right now, Tristan, is nothing.","index":254,"end_time":829.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":824.9,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":255,"end_time":831.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":830.9,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yep.","index":256,"end_time":833.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":832.66,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Or not much.","index":257,"end_time":833.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":833.18,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Or not much.","index":258,"end_time":835.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":834.74,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, I''ve, I''ve taken.","index":259,"end_time":837.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":835.62,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Oh, sorry.","index":260,"end_time":838.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":837.38,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''ve taken a few of these tiny little nurtures and put them into constant contact and I will give you guys access.","index":261,"end_time":843.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":838.06,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And it''s a poor man''s automated campaign.","index":262,"end_time":846.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":843.91,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Like it''s poor, but it''s, it''s actually successful.","index":263,"end_time":850.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":846.55,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, well, I mean, I think that''s the right step though.","index":264,"end_time":854.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":851.35,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I mean, you and I talked a little bit about that.","index":265,"end_time":855.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":854.35,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I mean, in, in the interim, it''s a good, it''s good route to take.","index":266,"end_time":859.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":855.95,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You know, we''re, we''re staying in touch and you''re getting information out to folks.","index":267,"end_time":864.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":859.83,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"There are a lot of different platforms, so I, I''m fine with that.","index":268,"end_time":867.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":864.27,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So one question.","index":269,"end_time":869.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":868.35,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So this is a Marketo form.","index":270,"end_time":870.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":869.39,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And so does this, once we get this information, does it integrate with Big marker at that point or how do we know.","index":271,"end_time":879.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":871.55,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It does?","index":272,"end_time":882.509,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":881.87,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It does at the moment, yes.","index":273,"end_time":883.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":882.51,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay.","index":274,"end_time":884.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":883.79,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So yeah, so that''s where Graziti, the Graziti Hawk team, the Venn diagram is a very slim crossover in the middle.","index":275,"end_time":894.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":884.19,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s critical, but it''s kind of slim.","index":276,"end_time":896.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":894.19,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So we have Justin who kind of oversees us if we need help.","index":277,"end_time":900.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":896.51,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But you know, Graziti works with, you know, James Kyle, you know, they''re in India.","index":278,"end_time":907.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":900.71,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Whoever they need to, to connect these forms before, during and after.","index":279,"end_time":912.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":908.39,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And when I say that it''s before the forms are in Marketo, then they register in Big marker, what happens after.","index":280,"end_time":919.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":912.31,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And then they, they put the emails in.","index":281,"end_time":921.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":919.99,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Like here''s an invite, a reminder, a follow up.","index":282,"end_time":924.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":921.87,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Once it flips on the website, James creates a new UTM link.","index":283,"end_time":930.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":924.07,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So we know if we put it on social, where it''s coming from, etc.","index":284,"end_time":933.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":930.7,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So that''s, that''s the goal.","index":285,"end_time":935.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":933.86,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Now.","index":286,"end_time":935.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":935.38,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Is it really working that way?","index":287,"end_time":937.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":935.66,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''m suspect it seems pretty manual for an automated series.","index":288,"end_time":942.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":937.22,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, I''m wondering if.","index":289,"end_time":944.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":943.14,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So the Marketo submission comes in.","index":290,"end_time":945.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":944.06,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''m wondering if those then get through like a web hook or something.","index":291,"end_time":949.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":945.74,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"They register in BigMarker or is that not automatic?","index":292,"end_time":951.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":949.26,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Do you know they do they register in BigMarker and then everyone receives their own personalized link.","index":293,"end_time":957.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":951.98,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay.","index":294,"end_time":958.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":958.12,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So yeah, we would have to see how that happens.","index":295,"end_time":962.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":959.08,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But, but makes sense.","index":296,"end_time":963.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":962.76,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So Marketo form capture data.","index":297,"end_time":966.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":964.44,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"They''re a user in Marketo at that point and then they get the unique URL to join.","index":298,"end_time":975.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":967.88,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, through Big marker.","index":299,"end_time":977.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":976.12,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And then they show up at 11 and then after that you''re saying it becomes an on demand scenario.","index":300,"end_time":985.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":977.88,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And, and how is that done now?","index":301,"end_time":989.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":986.32,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Is that through Big marker or is that something you would do through Marketo as a follow up?","index":302,"end_time":994.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":989.92,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, it''s done through Big marker.","index":303,"end_time":997.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":995.68,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Graziti assists in doing that for the people right now who do do physically attend.","index":304,"end_time":1004.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":997.92,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We score them poorly, but we do score them to say if you attend, here''s what that registration and attendance, whether you open the email, the three emails, etc, here''s how these stack up.","index":305,"end_time":1017.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1004.8,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And that is integrated into Salesforce.","index":306,"end_time":1020.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1017.49,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And then that report link into Salesforce goes over to the BDR team.","index":307,"end_time":1025.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1020.85,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So I pulled and it''s still quite manual.","index":308,"end_time":1028.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1025.73,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I pulled a list out of Big marker.","index":309,"end_time":1030.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1028.49,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I clean it up, I give them the Salesforce link.","index":310,"end_time":1033.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1030.69,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"They look into the activity in the scoring log to say, okay, do I call this person?","index":311,"end_time":1038.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1034.13,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Is it really like do I.","index":312,"end_time":1039.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1038.01,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"They make the determination whether they call them or not.","index":313,"end_time":1041.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1039.49,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Now they do call them or email them and then if they hit a certain score, which is 100, which is very vague why, but the hundred level, then they''re an automatic MQL which we, we register every day in a B, in a BI tool at a Salesforce.","index":314,"end_time":1058.829,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1041.81,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay.","index":315,"end_time":1060.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1059.47,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So there''s a lot of steps for very little in my opinion.","index":316,"end_time":1063.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1060.35,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But yeah, well, I mean it''s a good flow for us to understand because you know, we, we can.","index":317,"end_time":1072.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1063.95,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So are you sticking with Big Marker moving forward?","index":318,"end_time":1075.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1072.39,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"How''s that work?","index":319,"end_time":1076.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1075.43,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We don''t have to.","index":320,"end_time":1077.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1076.71,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We have it.","index":321,"end_time":1078.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1077.83,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And Colin.","index":322,"end_time":1079.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1078.71,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Hi Colin.","index":323,"end_time":1080.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1079.91,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Colin now has it and you have, you guys have access to it.","index":324,"end_time":1083.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1080.87,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So I mean it''s fine.","index":325,"end_time":1086.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1084.71,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''d never used it before.","index":326,"end_time":1087.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1086.15,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s painfully simple.","index":327,"end_time":1088.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1087.23,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I mean it''s.","index":328,"end_time":1089.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1088.83,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, well, you just mentioned Riverside in lieu of.","index":329,"end_time":1092.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1089.47,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I wasn''t sure if that was if you were using both of those differently or one was replacing the other.","index":330,"end_time":1098.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1092.51,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, we''re open to either.","index":331,"end_time":1101.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1099.44,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Whatever keeps the, the tech stack clean, as clean as humanly possible.","index":332,"end_time":1107.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1101.36,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You know, we don''t.","index":333,"end_time":1108.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1107.6,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We have all of these things that are, you should see our last pass.","index":334,"end_time":1112.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1108.56,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It is, it''s pages long and we''re starting to retire a bunch of things that we''re just not using.","index":335,"end_time":1117.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1112.12,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So Riverside, we won''t, you know, we won''t activate it until December 1st.","index":336,"end_time":1123.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1117.68,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So if you guys make the determination that, you know, once you take a look at the full stack to say, well, you know, this one is complementary, these two are fighting each other, then, then we can make the determination to get rid of one or the other.","index":337,"end_time":1135.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1124.41,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, I think for us a lot of times you can have, you know, a couple things that are feeding.","index":338,"end_time":1140.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1135.77,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s always good to just standardize the.","index":339,"end_time":1142.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1140.17,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"The event.","index":340,"end_time":1142.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1142.13,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So like the, the source might be big marker, but like what is.","index":341,"end_time":1146.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1143.05,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s a webinar.","index":342,"end_time":1147.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1146.25,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Right.","index":343,"end_time":1147.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1147.13,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So you could have, you know, we just want to make sure we define what that is and then what happens if.","index":344,"end_time":1152.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1147.53,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"If they attended a webinar as an activity, you know, where does that go?","index":345,"end_time":1156.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1152.45,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Does that trigger an increase in their lead score, etc.","index":346,"end_time":1161.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1156.83,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So for this one, Barb, you have the landing page set up the forms there.","index":347,"end_time":1165.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1161.99,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Is this live?","index":348,"end_time":1167.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1166.47,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Have you pushed this out yet?","index":349,"end_time":1169.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1167.75,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, it''s live.","index":350,"end_time":1170.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1169.67,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay.","index":351,"end_time":1171.269,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1170.71,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And so you mentioned afterward there''s nowhere to put the asset.","index":352,"end_time":1177.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1171.51,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So is that the best place for us to help on this one or what do you.","index":353,"end_time":1180.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1177.11,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Or is it more of like a strategy?","index":354,"end_time":1181.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1180.35,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Like where would this fit into the website?","index":355,"end_time":1183.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1181.91,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"What''s the best way to, to work with you there?","index":356,"end_time":1186,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1183.67,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, I think for this one, I''d like it to be a program.","index":357,"end_time":1189.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1186.56,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Right now what''s going to happen with this is it''s going to get buried in, in on demand webinars, which, you know, we have content mapping tomorrow, which is going to take us a long time.","index":358,"end_time":1201.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1189.2,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But I''ve gone through and I''ll share it with you guys, but you know, there''s, there''s no rhyme or reason where these things are put.","index":359,"end_time":1208.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1201.52,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And this is better.","index":360,"end_time":1209.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1208.68,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I actually fixed this whole thing.","index":361,"end_time":1210.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1209.48,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So resources used to just be one page.","index":362,"end_time":1213.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1210.96,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":363,"end_time":1214.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1213.54,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And.","index":364,"end_time":1214.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1214.02,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But you know, I''m just going through like if you go to webinars, all the on demand webinars.","index":365,"end_time":1220.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1214.9,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Well, I don''t, I have no idea if they''re relevant or not or if any.","index":366,"end_time":1227.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1220.86,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We, I.","index":367,"end_time":1228.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1227.7,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We don''t even track if.","index":368,"end_time":1230.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1228.579,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''m sure we do somewhere, but we don''t even track if anybody fills out the on demand nothing that marketing can see.","index":369,"end_time":1236.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1231.3,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"If it goes into Salesforce and we happen to get another mql, I have to go looking for it in on Demand.","index":370,"end_time":1243.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1237.06,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So getting back to the four pillars, what I''d love, it''s a whims program.","index":371,"end_time":1246.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1243.25,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Whims is our flagship and I''d love to be able to showcase that program and all of like, unfortunately, we''re not going to be able to redo the entire website for 2026, but we can get rid of things because this is a bit of an eyesore.","index":372,"end_time":1264.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1247.01,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":373,"end_time":1266.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1266.21,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So there are a couple things there.","index":374,"end_time":1267.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1266.57,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I mean, we''ll talk about it, but yeah, some connective tissue between the product and the content would be nice.","index":375,"end_time":1274.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1267.61,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You know, like have A have a block where it''s like featured webinar or featured knowledge series around whims which could be a content block that we, we fit in and then maybe some way here, you know, I like what you''ve done here, but you envision, you don''t know if this is enough.","index":376,"end_time":1296.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1274.91,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Maybe that we''re filtering by product, it needs to stand out even more.","index":377,"end_time":1300.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1296.15,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I think so.","index":378,"end_time":1301.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1300.9,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":379,"end_time":1302.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1301.7,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And, and again, I''m not even sure that these things are a relevant or right now if they''re labeled correctly.","index":380,"end_time":1309.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1302.02,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s, you know, I''m not going to eat up our time showing you now, but I''ve gone through every sheet of paper we''ve got over the last few weeks and it''s like they''re labeled incorrectly or you know, this is good news and bad news.","index":381,"end_time":1323.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1310.1,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You know, over night I found 13 case studies that are brand new sitting in brand folder that, you know.","index":382,"end_time":1331.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1323.42,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"No, we''d rather have the 2017 ones on the website.","index":383,"end_time":1333.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1331.14,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Oh goodness.","index":384,"end_time":1334.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1334.02,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You got some like good stuff that''s on the shelf right now.","index":385,"end_time":1338.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1334.9,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s awesome.","index":386,"end_time":1338.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1338.02,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And every single one of those case studies have, can be put into quote cards and social posts and it''s, it''s all data.","index":387,"end_time":1345.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1338.86,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s all, it''s all quantitative data and it''s like where have these been?","index":388,"end_time":1350.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1345.78,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"How did I miss those?","index":389,"end_time":1352.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1351.31,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":390,"end_time":1353.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1352.43,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"What''s the best way?","index":391,"end_time":1356.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1354.99,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Because I think we could, we could like just analyze how, how the website''s constructed now and make some, some recommendations on how to get this series to stand out a bit.","index":392,"end_time":1367.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1356.07,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Would that be the best so more of like a, like a analysis in a recommendation document.","index":393,"end_time":1373.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1367.31,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Is that maybe the best way?","index":394,"end_time":1374.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1373.71,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And then we could say how we would execute it or what do you think?","index":395,"end_time":1377.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1374.91,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":396,"end_time":1378.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1377.75,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"For next steps.","index":397,"end_time":1378.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1378.03,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That sounds, that sounds good.","index":398,"end_time":1379.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1378.71,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, that''s, that''s great.","index":399,"end_time":1381.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1379.87,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And I think starting with whims, we just don''t have enough activity.","index":400,"end_time":1384.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1381.19,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And now that I know we have content, I didn''t think we had any content.","index":401,"end_time":1387.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1384.83,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And we have tons of content.","index":402,"end_time":1388.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1387.75,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":403,"end_time":1389.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1389.07,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And we can share what those things are.","index":404,"end_time":1392.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1389.63,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You know, I think dashboards will be one compliant.","index":405,"end_time":1396.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1393.79,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I don''t know.","index":406,"end_time":1397.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1396.83,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I don''t know what the modules are.","index":407,"end_time":1398.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1397.31,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I know there were four of them to start, but I think just elevating that program and then creating, but kind of blowing out the program, you know, we just have, I just have the concept right now of the pillars and what I want to do with them.","index":408,"end_time":1411.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1398.43,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But the 25th is our first stab at anything.","index":409,"end_time":1414.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1411.53,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Got it.","index":410,"end_time":1416.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1415.73,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay.","index":411,"end_time":1416.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1416.21,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Well, I like it.","index":412,"end_time":1417.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1416.85,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You''re getting the ball rolling.","index":413,"end_time":1418.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1417.49,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But Then keeping your eyes on like what''s next, which we can, we can help you with.","index":414,"end_time":1422.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1418.49,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So.","index":415,"end_time":1422.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1422.29,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":416,"end_time":1423.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1422.65,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"All right, so we''ll.","index":417,"end_time":1424.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1423.65,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That''ll be the part one and basically analyze the, the existing site structure.","index":418,"end_time":1429.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1424.65,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And then what would we recommend to how to kind of like take this first step in a whims program.","index":419,"end_time":1436.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1429.41,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Right.","index":420,"end_time":1436.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1436.61,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"How can we then build it out?","index":421,"end_time":1438.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1436.93,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Where would it go on the website?","index":422,"end_time":1439.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1438.05,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"How can we connect the dots a little bit so we can draw that up and that might be come in the form of you maybe like a slightly revised site map where we say, hey, here''s where you could fit, you know, this type of program in.","index":423,"end_time":1454.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1440.45,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Here''s some of the language we could put around it and how it would be built out.","index":424,"end_time":1457.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1454.33,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And we''ll also look on the back end of the WordPress website because one of the things I would like to see is for doing like custom post types or anything for that because that would then allow us to maybe dynamically link from the WIMS product page, you know, for instance.","index":425,"end_time":1472.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1458.13,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Sure.","index":426,"end_time":1472.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1472.52,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We''re able to pull the latest in the series or something.","index":427,"end_time":1475.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1472.88,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So we''ll see how that''s built out right now.","index":428,"end_time":1478.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1475.92,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay.","index":429,"end_time":1480.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1479.88,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Anything else on that bullet point one that you had there?","index":430,"end_time":1484.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1480.44,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I don''t think so.","index":431,"end_time":1485.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1484.76,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I think that was probably the longest one.","index":432,"end_time":1488.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1485.6,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I mean the other two, I think I have a newsletter in there.","index":433,"end_time":1490.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1488.32,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We don''t have anywhere to opt into anything on our website.","index":434,"end_time":1495.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1491.32,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Well, we do on the forums.","index":435,"end_time":1496.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1495.54,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You have to agree, of course.","index":436,"end_time":1497.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1496.66,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But you know, I actually have people, you know, sending us a note saying can you add me to your newsletter?","index":437,"end_time":1503.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1497.7,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''m like, yeah, you can as soon as we have one.","index":438,"end_time":1507.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1503.38,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But that''s what I thought we.","index":439,"end_time":1510.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1507.54,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You know, again, when I put together the second sow for you guys, it kind of dove straight into nurture content execution, whereas, you know, we''re missing these infrastructure pieces to be able to do that.","index":440,"end_time":1523.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1510.34,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So I think newsletter is just another avenue to do that we want to put together.","index":441,"end_time":1527.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1524.41,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I mean, goodness knows we have enough stuff to talk about.","index":442,"end_time":1531.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1528.25,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We just aren''t.","index":443,"end_time":1532.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1531.69,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We''re just not.","index":444,"end_time":1534.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1533.77,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So.","index":445,"end_time":1535.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1534.73,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, and I''m wondering, Barb, if.","index":446,"end_time":1537.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1535.13,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Because once, because you mentioned nothing''s really happening, when folks do come to the webinar and you envision a nurture, do you envision that webinar register or attend kicks off a linear sequence or do you think they fall into a.","index":447,"end_time":1552.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1538.09,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"More of a newsletter where it''s, it''s always on go, you know what I''m saying?","index":448,"end_time":1558.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1554.22,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"They get it every month and you stay in front of that way or do you envision it''s like signed up for event, you know, virtual event attend.","index":449,"end_time":1566.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1558.5,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And then I get like these eight, you know, pieces of content that we map out after that.","index":450,"end_time":1571.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1566.54,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Like, which way do you think that goes?","index":451,"end_time":1574.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1571.98,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Does that make sense?","index":452,"end_time":1575.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1575.02,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Like one''s like linear, the other''s more ongoing.","index":453,"end_time":1578.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1575.82,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, I think, you know, I envision linear to start.","index":454,"end_time":1581.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1579.36,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You know, it may be overboard, but right now we have no volume whatsoever.","index":455,"end_time":1585.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1581.92,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And so if we''re just waiting for a monthly newsletter or a quarterly one that doesn''t come, then I don''t think that solves that problem, you know, that engagement problem.","index":456,"end_time":1594.639,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1585.52,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And you know, when I say newsletter, it''s just we do one internally.","index":457,"end_time":1600,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1594.8,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Well, it''s not beautiful, but I mean it''s, if you look at the content on it, it''s like we don''t tell anybody externally about all the things we''ve done.","index":458,"end_time":1608.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1600.32,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I mean, I think this month we had six regional user groups and you know, we''re in magazines and well, there''s, there''s nowhere to.","index":459,"end_time":1616.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1608.58,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Unless I''m doing it one off, which I wouldn''t do for all of those things.","index":460,"end_time":1620.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1616.86,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We have some major things that we want to talk about in a newsletter and then hey, in case you missed it, here''s a bunch of other things.","index":461,"end_time":1626.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1620.62,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But that''s why I think it''s linear to start.","index":462,"end_time":1628.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1626.82,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But we can, you know, once the volume gets up there, you know, we can take a look at that.","index":463,"end_time":1633.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1628.98,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And do you think that sequence kicks off in Marketo or is this something that we would build out to pull into HubSpot?","index":464,"end_time":1641.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1634.25,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Like what''s the.","index":465,"end_time":1641.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1641.05,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Because the event is on the 25th this month.","index":466,"end_time":1645.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1642.65,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And then do you think that sequence is when does that kick off or what do you envision there?","index":467,"end_time":1652.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1645.29,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, it''s already slightly kicked off.","index":468,"end_time":1655.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1652.73,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So you know, we want to get rid of Marketo, right?","index":469,"end_time":1658.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1655.13,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So we, we don''t want to.","index":470,"end_time":1659.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1658.49,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"This is the last one I have scheduled in Marketo for the.","index":471,"end_time":1663.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1659.69,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Is on the 25th.","index":472,"end_time":1664.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1663.75,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And so I think we get our instance shortly for HubSpot, whether, you know, for implementation, whenever we''re ready to do that.","index":473,"end_time":1673.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1664.95,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But basically it''s kicked off in a very simplistic fashion.","index":474,"end_time":1679.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1673.11,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So in Marketo, the invite, the reminder and the follow up is already scheduled.","index":475,"end_time":1684.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1679.79,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"The Salesforce report is already there, big marker implemented.","index":476,"end_time":1690,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1685.11,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I have it ready to go in constant contact because I don''t want to put it back into Marketo afterwards.","index":477,"end_time":1695.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1690.4,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So.","index":478,"end_time":1697.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1696.64,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Because I envision maybe it''s 100 people.","index":479,"end_time":1699.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1697.04,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So yeah, again it''s, it''s not sophisticated, but I envision this One through Marketo and then we''ll stop.","index":480,"end_time":1707.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1699.44,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay, got that.","index":481,"end_time":1709.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1707.92,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So how can we help?","index":482,"end_time":1710.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1709.36,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Are we helping you maybe design in constant contact for these 100 people?","index":483,"end_time":1715.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1710.72,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Because.","index":484,"end_time":1715.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1715.09,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And I like it.","index":485,"end_time":1716.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1715.77,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Right.","index":486,"end_time":1716.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1716.45,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We''re essentially, we''re bridging between Marketo and HubSpot, but we''re not going backwards and still using Marketo for this.","index":487,"end_time":1723.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1716.69,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We''re pulling out these 100 people.","index":488,"end_time":1725.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1723.69,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Like it''s a workflow based on this single event.","index":489,"end_time":1728.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1726.25,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We''re still going to have the touch points.","index":490,"end_time":1730.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1729.05,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s just a matter of using a couple different tools to get that done Right.","index":491,"end_time":1733.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1730.649,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Before we have HubSpot, it sounds like.","index":492,"end_time":1735.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1733.85,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":493,"end_time":1736.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1735.85,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And I''m happy to give you guys constant contact.","index":494,"end_time":1739.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1736.21,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I can give it to you this afternoon.","index":495,"end_time":1740.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1739.69,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s not much, you know, I''ve taken a bunch of very small things, 100 people per external events or call an event.","index":496,"end_time":1748.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1740.89,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But we do a lot of sponsorships and her.","index":497,"end_time":1752.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1748.83,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Not a lot.","index":498,"end_time":1752.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1752.43,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"3.","index":499,"end_time":1753.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1752.95,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We have another one next week.","index":500,"end_time":1754.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1753.39,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So we anticipate 100, 150 people.","index":501,"end_time":1757.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1754.55,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So, you know, give you access and you can see what I''m doing.","index":502,"end_time":1760.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1757.55,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But it is very like step change, step change.","index":503,"end_time":1764.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1760.67,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Like it''s, it''s not sophisticated but it is working.","index":504,"end_time":1767.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1764.67,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Like we can see that it is having an effect.","index":505,"end_time":1770.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1768.03,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, but yeah, I get that too.","index":506,"end_time":1773.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1771.72,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"The interesting part about the sophistication is not like the level of marketing that''s.","index":507,"end_time":1777.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1773.8,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Happening, but all of the tools that need to be banded together to make.","index":508,"end_time":1781.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1777.8,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It happen versus, you know, Tristan, we.","index":509,"end_time":1783.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1781.2,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Can build a custom app to connect.","index":510,"end_time":1784.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1783.4,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"BigMarker to HubSpot if we want to stick with BigMarker and then everything flows seamlessly.","index":511,"end_time":1788.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1784.64,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, that''s the stuff that we''ll look into.","index":512,"end_time":1791.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1789.16,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And yeah, like simple webhook, they attend.","index":513,"end_time":1796.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1793.64,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You know what, there''s all that, that, that will be available to us.","index":514,"end_time":1799.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1797.02,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So I think what we can do with, with this one, Barb, they will work with you.","index":515,"end_time":1807.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1801.42,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So they attend.","index":516,"end_time":1809.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1808.46,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"They have the.","index":517,"end_time":1810.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1809.82,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So the follow up email comes from Big Marker or does that come from Constant Contact?","index":518,"end_time":1815.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1810.78,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Do you think the, the first follow up will come from Mercado and that''s just to the people who registered but didn''t attend.","index":519,"end_time":1825.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1815.82,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And I can, I don''t have to send that.","index":520,"end_time":1828.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1826.32,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I can put that through Constant Contact.","index":521,"end_time":1830.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1828.72,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"What I do afterwards is kind of start fresh and say, you know, I saw your interest in this and then I kind of pick it up from there.","index":522,"end_time":1837.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1830.48,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Because what''s happening right now is, you know, we''ll send a follow up which just says, oh, here''s your link in case you missed it and then it goes to the BDR team.","index":523,"end_time":1845.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1837.84,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"They make three attempts, retire it, never talk to them again.","index":524,"end_time":1849.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1845.36,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yep.","index":525,"end_time":1850.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1850.36,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And so I take.","index":526,"end_time":1852.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1851,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I just make sure we''re sending them something, you know, so that''s why it''s going into constant contact and I''m inviting them to things and sending them links and, you know, it''s.","index":527,"end_time":1861.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1852.44,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And again, it''s not.","index":528,"end_time":1863,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1861.88,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"The approach is not that sophisticated, but it''s 100% more than what we''re doing right now.","index":529,"end_time":1869.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1864.68,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":530,"end_time":1869.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1869.48,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay.","index":531,"end_time":1870.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1870.2,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Well, if we can get constant contact access, we can get an idea how.","index":532,"end_time":1875.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1870.64,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"How those are set up now.","index":533,"end_time":1876.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1875.44,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And so the one that comes out of Marketo exists.","index":534,"end_time":1880.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1876.76,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And then after that, do you.","index":535,"end_time":1882.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1880.25,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Do you know what the content will be for the next touch point that happens after Marketo that you would launch it sounds like through constant contact at that point.","index":536,"end_time":1890.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1882.73,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"No, I haven''t created it yet.","index":537,"end_time":1892.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1890.73,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So.","index":538,"end_time":1893.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1893.21,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, no, I haven''t done it yet.","index":539,"end_time":1896.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1894.97,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"All right, cool.","index":540,"end_time":1897.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1896.49,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We can.","index":541,"end_time":1897.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1897.09,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Do you want us to help you build out something in constant contact?","index":542,"end_time":1900.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1897.53,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That way we.","index":543,"end_time":1901.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1900.89,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We know what you''re going for there and we could reproduce in HubSpot when that''s ready or what''s the best way to maybe step in and help there?","index":544,"end_time":1908.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1901.65,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Sure, we can do that.","index":545,"end_time":1910.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1909.03,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And it''s a.","index":546,"end_time":1911.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1910.31,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s a lot for your sow, I think, like, if.","index":547,"end_time":1913.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1911.59,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"If we only want to focus on this for November, cool by me.","index":548,"end_time":1917.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1913.95,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You know, I hadn''t put anything together yet.","index":549,"end_time":1921.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1918.95,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I figure anything after the 27th is, you know, for that week is a lost cause.","index":550,"end_time":1926.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1921.31,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Right.","index":551,"end_time":1926.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1926.23,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Because of the U. S. Thanksgiving holiday.","index":552,"end_time":1928.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1926.47,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So, yeah, you know, we just.","index":553,"end_time":1929.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1928.31,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We were going to park everything until first two weeks of December and then park everything again until January because nobody''s listening.","index":554,"end_time":1937.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1929.67,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But.","index":555,"end_time":1937.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1937.33,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, happy to.","index":556,"end_time":1939.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1938.33,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Because this is small, right?","index":557,"end_time":1940.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1939.29,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Like, it''s.","index":558,"end_time":1940.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1940.33,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s small, but if.","index":559,"end_time":1941.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1940.81,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"If it''s small enough to get a little bit of traction and get it right, then I think that''s the goal.","index":560,"end_time":1948.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1942.25,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Not.","index":561,"end_time":1948.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1948.49,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Not the leads themselves.","index":562,"end_time":1951.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1949.85,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":563,"end_time":1952.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1951.53,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Well, I like it just for the workflow.","index":564,"end_time":1953.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1952.01,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It helps us think through what happens when they attend an event.","index":565,"end_time":1957.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1953.73,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Like, what do we want to send them, what do we want them to see, where do they go?","index":566,"end_time":1961.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1957.01,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I mean, it''s just a good exercise for us to know.","index":567,"end_time":1963.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1961.05,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It helps us plan, like the bigger overarching HubSpot implementation as well.","index":568,"end_time":1969.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1965,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Like what.","index":569,"end_time":1969.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1969.28,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"What data events do we want to track and all that.","index":570,"end_time":1972.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1969.76,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So I think it''s exercise for us.","index":571,"end_time":1974.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1972.36,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"For this newsletter.","index":572,"end_time":1975.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1974.76,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Do you envision lead scoring tied to that as well, Barb?","index":573,"end_time":1978.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1975.72,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I do, yeah.","index":574,"end_time":1979.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1978.36,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay, so.","index":575,"end_time":1980.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1979.2,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And I know we''re at Time guys, just so you know, on, you know, the content mapping, we start that tomorrow, Monday, you know, going through source.","index":576,"end_time":1990.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1980.6,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Like right now we have what two sources that we, we track.","index":577,"end_time":1994.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1990.55,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Email and trade show, I think.","index":578,"end_time":1999.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1995.27,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But I put together, I think I''m up to 12 or 15 sources that says, well this is outbound, this is a paid ad.","index":579,"end_time":2004.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1999.43,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"This is like so just trying to get alignment on what those are and then what lead definitions are and then the scoring.","index":580,"end_time":2010.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2004.71,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So that''s a three part conversation starting Monday that I''ll loop you guys into after the first call.","index":581,"end_time":2016.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2010.63,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But yeah, so we thought we''re going to redo the scoring but we had to start with the definitions first.","index":582,"end_time":2022.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2016.31,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Like we''re just, we''re skipping the whole top of the funnel.","index":583,"end_time":2025.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2022.62,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I love it.","index":584,"end_time":2026.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2025.9,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I mean that''s, that''s like.","index":585,"end_time":2027.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2026.54,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And I think we mentioned that on Friday''s call.","index":586,"end_time":2029.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2027.62,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Like that''s sometimes the hardest part is just the business process side and coming to an agreement.","index":587,"end_time":2034.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2029.66,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Like on the technical side we can figure out how to, how to implement it.","index":588,"end_time":2039.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2034.94,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But it''s like what is a lead?","index":589,"end_time":2040.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2039.46,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You know, so many different definitions.","index":590,"end_time":2043.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2041.1,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So.","index":591,"end_time":2044.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2043.9,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, and right now we don''t even know.","index":592,"end_time":2048.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2045.28,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Well, I saw something on, I saw something this morning from Kyle.","index":593,"end_time":2052.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2048.88,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"He''s redoing all his lead processes which, you know, I like to think you guys had something to do with that.","index":594,"end_time":2059.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2052.76,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I didn''t read it yet, but I saw that this morning.","index":595,"end_time":2061.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2059.08,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"He''s like updating all lead processes as of now.","index":596,"end_time":2064.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2062,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, good, good chats about that.","index":597,"end_time":2069.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2067.44,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I mean as far as next steps for us, like I do want to talk about like the HubSpot implementation.","index":598,"end_time":2073.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2069.2,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You know, basically our first, first deliverable is really a document where we map out a lot of the findings that we have and then some of the suggestions that, that we would make based on information we have.","index":599,"end_time":2084.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2073.76,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So there''s got to be a draft of that that gets to you and I''ll look at the dates we, we have.","index":600,"end_time":2088.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2084.63,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But it''s, we want to get it to you before Thanksgiving.","index":601,"end_time":2091.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2088.99,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So it''s like, hey, here''s, here''s everything that, that we have.","index":602,"end_time":2093.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2091.47,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"The one big thing I do just want to ask you or at least to plan a seed is I''m trying to figure out the in parallel piece because when we do have syncing involved, I want to know maybe how you envision that because Marketo is still syncing with Salesforce.","index":603,"end_time":2110.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2094.59,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And then obviously if we have HubSpot introduced, you know, we want to create rules right as to where the, the source of truth is.","index":604,"end_time":2118.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2110.76,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So that was the one Thing I wanted to talk.","index":605,"end_time":2121.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2118.16,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":606,"end_time":2122.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2122.16,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I think from.","index":607,"end_time":2124.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2122.56,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"From my vantage point, like for marketing as far as a push like we, you know, 20.","index":608,"end_time":2129.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2125.28,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Well, the 26th will be the cutoff for that because of this, you know, first pillar and then I don''t have anything scheduled from my perspective to.","index":609,"end_time":2140.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2130.5,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"To go out.","index":610,"end_time":2141.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2140.26,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Like, everything will be done from.","index":611,"end_time":2143.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2141.54,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"From my perspective.","index":612,"end_time":2144.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2143.62,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Now the forms though on the website are live and those are still linked in Marketo.","index":613,"end_time":2149.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2144.54,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So, you know, we''ll have to take a look at those.","index":614,"end_time":2152.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2149.14,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Maybe that''s in parallel to say, are we rebuilding those first?","index":615,"end_time":2155.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2152.42,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Because it''s not a lot.","index":616,"end_time":2157.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2155.7,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Like, I''m not put.","index":617,"end_time":2157.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2157.06,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I won''t be pushing a ton of people to those assets because, you know, I don''t want them to go there right now, which is so odd as a marketing person.","index":618,"end_time":2165.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2157.99,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But, you know, I''d rather they just go on us Thanksgiving and we''ll deal with it later.","index":619,"end_time":2170.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2165.55,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But yeah, it''s those forms that are tied to Marketo now.","index":620,"end_time":2173.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2170.43,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We don''t get a ton, but we do get some people coming into various sources.","index":621,"end_time":2179.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2173.75,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So there''s a lead hawk form that comes in which I think we touched upon briefly.","index":622,"end_time":2185.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2179.47,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But then there''s.","index":623,"end_time":2186.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2185.4,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And that.","index":624,"end_time":2186.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2186.12,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That doesn''t touch Marketo.","index":625,"end_time":2188.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2186.68,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So that one is live that we have to figure that out.","index":626,"end_time":2191.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2188.12,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But on the Marketo side, it''s the website forms.","index":627,"end_time":2194.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2191.92,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I think there''s.","index":628,"end_time":2195.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2194.96,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I mean, they''re in many places, but.","index":629,"end_time":2198.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2196.88,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''S like there''s under 10 total.","index":630,"end_time":2200.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2198.64,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I think there is.","index":631,"end_time":2201.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2200.4,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":632,"end_time":2202,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2201.64,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"They''re like live and functional.","index":633,"end_time":2203.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2202.08,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":634,"end_time":2204.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2203.64,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"There''s eight.","index":635,"end_time":2205.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2204.56,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay.","index":636,"end_time":2207.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2206.72,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And so, yeah, there''s some point.","index":637,"end_time":2209.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2207.84,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We''ll flip those over.","index":638,"end_time":2210.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2209.16,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":639,"end_time":2211.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2210.8,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"The big thing is like, when do we pull the plug on market syncing with Salesforce there?","index":640,"end_time":2218.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2211.16,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Because there will be some structural changes we''ll have to make because we''re talking through the lead object, which I don''t even know if we use moving forward.","index":641,"end_time":2225.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2218.22,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay.","index":642,"end_time":2226.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2225.74,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I think that goes away because HubSpot doesn''t even.","index":643,"end_time":2231.499,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2226.94,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You have to kind of make a choice as to whether contacts are going to become leads in Salesforce or Contact.","index":644,"end_time":2236.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2231.5,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It has to be one or the other because we.","index":645,"end_time":2240.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2236.22,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We don''t want to use the HubSpot lead object.","index":646,"end_time":2243.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2240.46,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That''s a whole different ball game because that requires the sales platform on top.","index":647,"end_time":2249.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2243.23,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So that''s like an extra subscription.","index":648,"end_time":2252.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2250.31,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That doesn''t really even help you all because.","index":649,"end_time":2253.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2252.03,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And we''ll write it up as to why.","index":650,"end_time":2257.029,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2255.11,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But like the leads don''t even really.","index":651,"end_time":2259.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2257.029,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s like an extra step almost for you all.","index":652,"end_time":2261.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2259.35,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I think if we could create them as contacts and classify them with a life cycle stage of lead kind of does the same thing.","index":653,"end_time":2267.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2261.15,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay.","index":654,"end_time":2268.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2268.48,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So.","index":655,"end_time":2269.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2269.04,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But we''ll, we''ll go through that.","index":656,"end_time":2271.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2269.32,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We''ll write it up as far as what we''re thinking, so.","index":657,"end_time":2273.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2271.36,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay, that sounds great.","index":658,"end_time":2275.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2274.08,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And I guess just the third thing on there was the resource section adding the videos.","index":659,"end_time":2279.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2276.32,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Just, you know, you can ignore that for now.","index":660,"end_time":2281.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2279.96,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We just, we don''t have any videos yet to put on there, so we''ll need it at some point.","index":661,"end_time":2287.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2281.68,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We have a massive program in place, but we won''t have those videos ready till December, so we can, we can skip it for now.","index":662,"end_time":2294.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2287.6,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"All right, sounds good.","index":663,"end_time":2296.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2295.22,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Well, thanks, Bart.","index":664,"end_time":2297.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2296.66,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Thanks for running over a few minutes.","index":665,"end_time":2298.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2297.34,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Appreciate you chatting here.","index":666,"end_time":2299.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2298.42,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We''ll, we''ll get working on, you know, that, that first piece as far as the analysis on, on what we do with, you know, these, these webinars that come through and go from there.","index":667,"end_time":2309.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2299.62,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Sounds good.","index":668,"end_time":2310.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2309.78,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Thanks, everybody.","index":669,"end_time":2310.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2310.34,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Appreciate it.","index":670,"end_time":2311.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2310.94,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Thank you, Barb.","index":671,"end_time":2312.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2311.54,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Cheers.","index":672,"end_time":2313.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2312.66,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Bye.","index":673,"end_time":2313.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2313.18,"speaker_name":null}],"dateString":"2025-11-13T14:57:10.000Z","host_email":null,"meeting_link":null,"participants":[],"transcript_url":"https://app.fireflies.ai/view/01K9YVGVKMFHGD1YY8RX6EJ2YB","organizer_email":"tristan.pelligrino@marketersindemand.com"}'::jsonb,
