  '[{"text":"Ask James for hosting details and potential staging environment for WordPress website (07:33)","completed":false},{"text":"Share newly found case studies and centralized content inventory with the team (21:40)","completed":false},{"text":"Provide Constant Contact access to the team to review current nurture sequences (31:01)","completed":false},{"text":"Confirm Marketo forms inventory and plan migration approach (35:00)","completed":false},{"text":"Conduct analysis of existing website structure to suggest improvements for the pillars program placement and visibility, including potential revised site map and custom post type implementation on WordPress (18:55)","completed":false},{"text":"Assist with designing and building nurture campaigns in Constant Contact as an interim step before HubSpot migration (31:01)","completed":false},{"text":"Collaborate on lead source definition and lead scoring framework during content mapping sessions starting Monday (33:35)","completed":false},{"text":"Help define syncing rules between Marketo, HubSpot, and Salesforce for lead/contact data and streamline lead process (35:00)","completed":false},{"text":"Manage marketing operations, including data migration, checking data and workflows related to HubSpot and current systems (00:00)","completed":false}]'::jsonb,
