_id":0,"start_time":1920.19,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"So I actually really like workforce management solution.","index":414,"end_time":1926.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1922.31,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I think PSA because of the other tools that are in the market almost puts you into a box.","index":415,"end_time":1930.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1926.03,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Whereas you have features that stand above a regular PSA tool especially with AI native capabilities.","index":416,"end_time":1937.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1930.27,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I think that''s a great way to frame the product.","index":417,"end_time":1940.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1938.43,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, maybe it is.","index":418,"end_time":1945.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1943.94,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"We can try that Workforce management and then we have some more.","index":419,"end_time":1950.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1945.7,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"What''s unique about Isadalo Integrated resource management skill based resource.","index":420,"end_time":1954.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1950.7,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"This is all terms that we use workforce management, complex AI search features and we''re actually building an AI agent which is pretty cool.","index":421,"end_time":1962.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1954.46,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Will be released soon actually I think on Monday is the first release.","index":422,"end_time":1966.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1962.5,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Nice.","index":423,"end_time":1967.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1966.74,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Compiling skills, availability development, demand data, staffing workflows.","index":424,"end_time":1971.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1967.18,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"This is actually one of the kind of the most used features.","index":425,"end_time":1977.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1971.58,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"I would say one of the reasons why?","index":426,"end_time":1978.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1977.22,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"All large companies like Fujitsu Computer Center T Systems and so use it.","index":427,"end_time":1983.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1978.58,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"It''s the global.","index":428,"end_time":1985.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1983.98,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"The staffing workflows in the global organization where not everyone can book everyone.","index":429,"end_time":1989.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1985.26,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"That''s only for enterprise customers though.","index":430,"end_time":1993.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1991.74,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"And then we have end to end process from sales to delivery.","index":431,"end_time":1997.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1995.07,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"CV parser, okay management, okay.","index":432,"end_time":1999.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1997.43,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Position.","index":433,"end_time":2000.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2000.35,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"And then I have some ideas just collected here.","index":434,"end_time":2003.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2000.75,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"So one of the idea for the.","index":435,"end_time":2008.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2006.43,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"What do we want to get to.","index":436,"end_time":2009.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2008.19,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Is to replace resource managers with AI agents.","index":437,"end_time":2013.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2009.07,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":